description: Try our easy to follow Carrots & Fennel Baked In Orange Juice & Honey recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Carrots & Fennel Baked In Orange Juice & Honey
name: Carrots & Fennel Baked In Orange Juice & Honey Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Remove lid. Increase heat to high. Cook until juices have evaporated. Transfer to a serving plate. Serve topped with dill and reserved fennel fronds.
